name: SONG FOR @discontentisimo
description:
-SOUND ON-

@discontentisimo is a friend of life, with a deep bond that unites us. He is a special person, with a unique sense of humor who can make a joke in difficult times. He has this beautiful and amazing project called “Augurio” (@augurio_augurio) and I invite you to check it out, it´s about imaging the future. For this special song he gave me a poem from Rubén Darío, “Sonatina”, and a musical interpretation of Jake Shimabukuro. This is my song for him…

Keys, Synth, Guitars & Bass: Dibaxu; Ukulele sample: Jake Shimabukuro

Dibaxu // tw: @dibaxuP

*This is a collection of special and dedicated song for those collectors that get #1, #2, #3 and #4 for my “Annotations” collection. If you get it, let me know and I will do something special for you, this is a lifetime offer.
